Practice 001

Make an HSE KPI generator app
Feature:
1. Generate HOC_ASLO styles (V1), generate Excel file HOC (V2)
2. Generate Crew Training KPI (V2)

-----
1. Generate HOC_ASLO styles
1.1 Input personnel names, event location and event date
1.2. Choose Job mode: Stanby mode, Rigup mode, Perfo Mode.
1.3. Program will assign HOC each personnel that suitable with the mode.
Program have database of HOC data with its Job type category.

1.4 Generate excel file, with correct file names, and correct format for ASLO HOC style.
1.5 Interface with the app via telegram

Database Design:
1. HOC_Content_Schema: 
-- id_HOC, (id of HOC)
-- description, (string: describe the finding)
-- action (string: describe the action item to resolve the finding)
-- hazard type (as per HOC aslo option)
-- job jobType mode (arr: standby, rigup, perfo, logging)
-- contributorName (string: name of HOC entry creator)
-- dateCreated(datetime)
-- dateModified(datetime)

2. JobType_Schema
-- id_jobType
-- jobType_name
-- content [array of id_HOC]
-- dateCreated(datetime)
-- dateModified(datetime)


____
Api Design

/newHOC
-- input new HOC entry
/generateHOC
-- input crew name, date, and jobType
-- count crew qty, select random HOC based on jobType 
-- assign selected HOC to each crew, set as array / object
-- generate filename.
-- send data to /get-excel
/getExcel
-- input HOC object
-- open HOC excel template
-- assign each object to each cell in excel
-- save as new excel file and send for download


____________

folder
- template excel
- generated excel
-- id

